---
---

<section class="bg-[#f0f9e5] text-zinc-950 py-24 md:py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-[1200px] relative z-10 text-center">
    
    <h2 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl uppercase tracking-tight leading-none mb-8 max-w-[900px] mx-auto">
      Grow 10X Faster, Better, Smarter.
    </h2>
    
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed max-w-[800px] mx-auto font-medium font-sans mb-16">
      Skip the guesswork, trial-and-error and never-ending shit show of trying to figure everything out yourself – for the very first time. And instead, grow your business with proven <span class="underline underline-offset-4">client-getting-funnels</span>, frameworks and <strong>scientific customer acquisition</strong> (not hopes and prayers).
    </p>

    <div class="relative w-full max-w-[1000px] mx-auto mt-20">
      
      <!-- Globe Wrapper Placeholder -->
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-[60%] w-full max-w-[800px] aspect-square bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(208,242,36,0.1)_0%,transparent_70%)] rounded-full -z-10 pointer-events-none">
        <!-- In a full implementation, a WebGL Globe script would inject here -->
      </div>

      <!-- Stats Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mt-32 md:mt-48 lg:mt-64 relative z-10">
        
        <!-- Stat 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center justify-center transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2 duration-300">
          <p class="text-zinc-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-2">Revenue Generated</p>
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-heading text-zinc-950 mb-4">$7.8<span class="text-4xl text-primary ml-1">B</span></div>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans font-medium">We let our numbers do the talking. $7.8 Billion in reported client revenue and counting.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Stat 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center justify-center transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2 duration-300">
          <p class="text-zinc-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-2">Size Of Our Platform</p>
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-heading text-zinc-950 mb-4">200<span class="text-4xl text-primary ml-1">K</span></div>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans font-medium">200,000 customers and counting make up our diverse and ever growing platform.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Stat 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center justify-center transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2 duration-300">
          <p class="text-zinc-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-2">Our Reach</p>
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-heading text-zinc-950 mb-4">136</div>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans font-medium">Serving customers in over 136 different countries.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Stat 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center justify-center transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2 duration-300">
          <p class="text-zinc-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-2">Battle Tested</p>
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-heading text-zinc-950 mb-4">1067</div>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans font-medium">Our strategies have been battle tested in over 1067 different industries and niches.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
